    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 6,
    "last_activity_date" : 1386814888,
    "last_edit_date" : 1386814888,
    "creation_date" : 1386813645,
    "answer_id" : 20533665,
    "question_id" : 4088080,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>An implementation found at <a href=\"http://ormlite.com/javadoc/ormlite-android/com/j256/ormlite/android/AndroidDatabaseResults.html#getBoolean%28int%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Ormlite Cursor</a> also checks for Null which none of the other answers do.</p>\n\n<pre><code>   public boolean getBoolean(int columnIndex) {\n        if (cursor.isNull(columnIndex) || cursor.getShort(columnIndex) == 0) {\n            return false;\n        } else {\n            return true;\n        }\n    }\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 1133400,
      "reputation" : 21,
      "user_id" : 1118956,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/478eed9b63d952e0a837ad69b273d5f3?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "RedBullet",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1118956/redbullet"
    },
    "is_accepted" : false,
    "score" : 2,
    "last_activity_date" : 1465305221,
    "last_edit_date" : 1465305221,
    "creation_date" : 1416498800,
    "answer_id" : 27043869,
    "question_id" : 4088080,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>boolean b = (cursor.getInt(cursor.getColumnIndex(\"item\")) != 0);</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3772408,
      "reputation" : 35669,
      "user_id" : 3134215,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 42,
      "profile_image" : "https://i.sstatic.net/D6VcW.jpg?s=256",
      "display_name" : "Ravi",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/3134215/ravi"
