    "body" : "<p>I face the same thing in kotlin.\nThere was the value &quot;true/false&quot; in the database\nand I access it with this code:</p>\n<pre><code>cursor.getString(4).toBoolean()\n</code></pre>\n<p>//first as a string then converting them to boolean</p>\n"
